HTML
&lt;div class=&quot;ui raised segment&quot;&gt;
  &lt;h2 class=&quot;ui header&quot;&gt;演示形式：具有自定义验证&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;form [formGroup]=&quot;myForm&quot;
        (ngSubmit)=&quot;onSubmit(myForm.value)&quot;
